com.fpsrobotics.interfaces

Interface ThreadsAndClasses

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Analog, DeviceMap, DIOs, Joysticks, Relays, Solenoids, Talons
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Hackbots

    public interface ThreadsAndClasses
extends DIOs, Joysticks, Relays, Talons, Analog, Solenoids
    Where threads and classes can be instantiated, so they can be easily changed. This interface extends all others so the classes can be given variables from other interfaces.
    Author:
    ray
